title: Prada Symbole Sunglasses Black (SPR17W_E1AB_F05S0_C_049)
description:
The Prada Symbole Sunglasses Black (SPR17W_E1AB_F05S0_C_049) are a stylish and contemporary eyewear option that embodies the brand's commitment to innovation and luxury.

These Prada sunglasses make a bold fashion statement while providing excellent sun protection with their sleek design and careful attention to detail. Their frame is crafted from high-quality acetate, a durable and lightweight material that ensures comfort and longevity. Their dark gray lenses are carefully selected to provide 100% UV protection, shielding the eyes from harmful sun rays while maintaining optical clarity. A black colorway gives the sunglasses a classic and versatile nature, making them suitable for any number of occasions. This accessory comes in a universal fit.

What our experts agree is the standout feature of the Prada Symbole Sunglasses Black (SPR17W_E1AB_F05S0_C_049) is the symmetrical metal detailing on the temples, which showcases the iconic Prada logo. These sunglasses originally retailed with a price tag of $520.

title: Whoop 5.0 Coreknit Jet Black Band (12 Month Peak Subscription Included)
description:
The WHOOP 5.0 is a next-generation fitness and health wearable designed to optimize your performance, recovery, and sleep — all without a screen. Lightweight and discreet, it continuously monitors key metrics like heart rate variability (HRV), resting heart rate, skin temperature, blood oxygen, and sleep quality. The 5.0 also features Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE) broadcasting, haptic alarms, and enhanced sensors for improved accuracy.

With 24/7 data tracking and personalized coaching through the WHOOP app, you'll gain deep insights into your strain, recovery, and sleep to perform at your peak — whether you're an athlete, high-performer, or health enthusiast. The device comes with WHOOP Body® apparel integration for ultimate comfort and style.

Key Features:

Advanced sensor suite for more accurate health insights

Strain, recovery, and sleep tracking with personalized coaching

BLE broadcasting to connect with other devices

Haptic feedback for silent alarms and alerts

Skin temperature and SpO2 monitoring

Waterproof and chargeable while you wear it

Optional WHOOP Body® smart apparel compatibility

Includes 5.0 Device, Wireless PowerPack, SuperKnit Obsidian Band, and a Superknit Luxe Obsidian with Titanium Band. (You'll receive an Superknit Luxe Obsidian with Titanium Band, Obsidian Superknit Band, wireless PowerPack, and WHOOP 5.0 device. All WHOOP devices are covered under a lifetime warranty.)

Lightweight and discreet, it continuously monitors key metrics like heart rate variability (HRV), resting heart rate, skin temperature, blood oxygen, and sleep quality. The 5.0 also features Bluetooth Low Energy (BLE) broadcasting, haptic alarms, and enhanced sensors for improved accuracy.

With 24/7 data tracking and personalized coaching through the WHOOP app, you'll gain deep insights into your strain, recovery, and sleep to perform at your peak — whether you're an athlete, high-performer, or health enthusiast. The device comes with WHOOP Body® apparel integration for ultimate comfort and style.

Key Features:

Advanced sensor suite for more accurate health insights

Strain, recovery, and sleep tracking with personalized coaching

BLE broadcasting to connect with other devices

Haptic feedback for silent alarms and alerts

Skin temperature and SpO2 monitoring

Waterproof and chargeable while you wear it

Optional WHOOP Body® smart apparel compatibility

Includes 5.0 Device, Wireless PowerPack, SuperKnit Obsidian Band, and a Rush Sportflex Band. (You'll receive an Obsidian SuperKnit band, Rush Sportflex Band, wireless PowerPack, and WHOOP 5.0 device. All WHOOP devices are covered under a lifetime warranty.)

title: Louis Vuitton x Nigo Earphone Case Damier Ebene Giant Brown
description:
Virgil Abloh has joined forces with Japanese streetwear legend NIGO to release a collaborative capsule collection called LV², marking Virgil's first collaboration at Louis Vuitton since joining in 2018 as the Men's Artistic Director. The Louis Vuitton NIGO collaboration launched worldwide in June 2020. Staying true to the Maison's codes, the two designers have fused their approach to fashion in an assortment of pieces across bags, accessories, apparel, and footwear. The Louis Vuitton, Earphones Case, gets a refresh with the Giant Damier Ebene canvas, stamped with an LV Made signature mallard duck, a graphic commonly used in NIGO's brand Human Made. The earphones case features silver-color hardware, a zip-around closure and snap hook closure. The Louis Vuitton NIGO Earphones Case, Giant Damier Ebene retailed for $590 at the time of release; it measures 2.6 in x 2.6 in x 1.4 in, and the Louis Vuitton Style Number is GI0494. No earphones included.

Please Note: Dust bag and box are not required for this accessory.

description: The Pop Mart Labubu The Monsters Coca-Cola Series Vinyl Face Single Blind Box is a playful collectible that merges Labubu’s quirky charm with the iconic Coca-Cola brand. title: Pop Mart Labubu The Monsters Big into Energy Series Vinyl Plush Pendant Single Blind Box Pack of 1
description:
The Pop Mart Labubu The Monsters Big into Energy Series Vinyl Plush Pendant Sealed Case was released on April 24, 2025, for a retail price of $168 USD. Pop Mart, the Chinese collectibles powerhouse founded in 2010, continues to dominate the designer toy scene with creative vinyl figures and plushies that have become must-haves for collectors. The Labubu Big into Energy series is a standout—perfect for longtime fans and a great entry point for those new to the hobby.

Building on the Labubu universe, this set features six themed figures—Love, Happiness, Loyalty, Serenity, Hope, and Luck—each tied to the five elements: Metal, Wood, Water, Fire, and Earth. A mystery secret figurine adds to the thrill of the chase. Each collectible is crafted using a random tie-dye technique, making every figure a unique gradient masterpiece.

title: Pop Mart Labubu The Monsters Have a Seat Vinyl Plush Sealed Case Pack of 1
description:
Be surprised by what’s inside this blind box of Pop Mart Labubu The Monsters Have A Seat Vinyl Plush Blind Box. The appeal of this worldwide craze lies not just in the quirky design of these beloved characters, but also in the appeal of never quite knowing which Labubu you’ll get.

The vinyl and plush Labubu collectibles have created an obsession worldwide—and the Monsters Have A Seat collection is no different. Designed by Hong Kong’s alternative designer, Kasing Lung, the Labubu series features toothy-grinned, sassy monsters that are cute, chaotic, and filled with attitude. Perfect for ages 15 and up, these sitting toys average about 6 inches in height. Look out for sharp teeth, mischievous eyes, and cool little outfits from your Labubu, no matter what you get in the blind box.

The set could include a miniature Labubu plushie with soft fur in light pink, baby blue, pale green, chocolate brown, cream, light gray, or beige. Each color mimics the pastel hue of a sweet macaroon. In addition, the plushie features a durable vinyl face and a key ring attachment. The key ring is crafted from gold-tone metal, and the ribbon attachment features "THE MONSTERS" in bold lettering.

Louis Vuitton x Nigo Duck Figurine Brown
description:
Virgil Abloh has joined forces with Japanese streetwear legend NIGO to release a collaborative capsule collection called LV², marking Virgil's first collaboration at Louis Vuitton since joining in 2018 as the Men's Artistic Director. The Louis Vuitton NIGO collaboration launched worldwide in June 2020. Staying true to the Maison's codes, the two designers have fused their approach to fashion in an assortment of pieces across bags, accessories, apparel, and footwear. The Louis Vuitton, Duck Figurine, is an eye-catching collectible that showcases the LV Made signature mallard duck, one of many graphics commonly used in NIGO's brand Human Made. The Duck Figurine is made of Corian with the iconic Louis Vuitton Monogram Canvas on the underside of the piece. The Louis Vuitton NIGO Duck Figurine measures 5.9 in x 3.9 in x 1.6 in and retailed for $1,160 at the time of release; the Louis Vuitton Style Number is GI0521.

description:
The Off-White Off Doormat is an Italian-made rug designed by the late American fashion designer Virgin Alboh's Off-White label.

This circular, 26-inch, black, and cream doormat was released as part of a three-piece rug collection by Off-White in the 3rd quarter of the year. It features a spherical logo with the words "OFF" in bold, a contrasting border, and a raised weave. Additionally, it features a rubber backing, which protects it from developing curls.

The Off-White Off Doormat was released on the 1st of August, 2021. At the time of its release, this product had a retail price of $150.
